                  <Text layoutX="65.0" layoutY="1631.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Semantic HTML gives meaning to the structure. Examples: &lt;header&gt;, &lt;footer&gt;, &lt;article&gt;, &lt;nav&gt;, &lt;main&gt;." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
