                  <Text layoutX="54.0" layoutY="753.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="There are also self-closing tags that don’t need a closing pair, like &lt;img&gt; and &lt;br&gt;." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
